snippet.title: Project Timi: Sasha's Curse - Official Trailer #2 | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Watch the trailer for Project Timi Sasha's Curse, a 3D rhythmic puzzle action game developed by Ephemeral Cube. Players will use rhythmic music to engage magic traps, fight enemies, and explore dream worlds to reveal the secrets within Lucity Town. Project Timi Sasha's Curse is coming soon to Nintendo Switch and PC (Steam).
